ishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016170, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "My God, my Lord, this Muhammad is your messenger, this Ali is the cousin of your Prophet and this Hasan and Husain are the grandsons of your Prophet. My God, send down upon us from the heavens the same table of food as You sent down upon Bani Israel; but they ate from it and then denied the bounty. O Allah, send it upon us and we would remain steadfast on faith.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Parwardigaar! Ay mere Mawla, yeh Tere nabi Muhammad (s.a.w.a) hai aur yeh Ali (a.s) Tere Nabi ke chacha-zaad bhai hai, yeh Hasan (a.s) aur Husain (a.s) hai jo Tere Nabi ke nawaase hai. Parwardigaar! Ham par Maaedah (dastarkhwaan) naazil farma jis tarah Nabi'e Israaeel par naazil farmaaya tha, un logo’n ne usey khaaya aur kufraan'e ne’mat ki. Parwardigaar Tu usey ham par naazil farma, ham us par imaan rakhte hai.", "Urdu": "اے پروردگار، اے میرے مولا، یہ آپ کے نبی محمد ہیں اور یہ علی آپ کے نبی کے چچا زاد بھائی ہیں یہ حسن اور حسین ہیں جو آپ کے نبی کے نواسے ہیں۔ پروردگار ہم پر مائدہ نازل فرما جس طرح بنی اسرائیل پر نازل فرمایا تھا ان لوگوں نے اسے کھایا اور کفران نعمت کی۔ پیروردگار تو اسے ہم پر نازل فرما ہم اس پر ایمان رکھتے ہیں۔", "RArabic": "ELAAHEE WA SAYYEDEE, HAAZAA MOHAMMADUN NABIYYOKA, WA HAAZAA A’LIYYUN IBNO A’MME NABIYYEKA, WA HAAZAANIL HASANO WAL HUSAYNO SIBTAA NABIYYEKA. ELAAHEE ANZIL A’LAYNAA MAA-EDATAN MENAS SAMAA-E KAMAA ANZALTAHAA A’LAA BANEE ISRAA-EELA AKALOO MINHAA WA KAFAROO BEHAA, ALLAAHUMMA ANZILHAA A’LAYNAA FA-INNAA BEHAA MOAMENOON.", "ArabicText1": "اِلٰهِیْ وَسَیِّدِیْ هٰذَا مُحَمَّدٌ نَبِیُّكَ، وَهٰذَا عَلِیٌّ اِبْنُ عَمِّ نَبِیِّكَ، وَهٰذَانِ الْحَسَنُ وَالْحُسَیْنُ سِبْطَا بَبِیِّكَ۔ اِلٰهِیْ اَنْزِلْ عَلَیْنَا مَاۗئِدَۃً مِّنَ السَّمَاۗءِ كَمَا اَنْزَلْتَهَا عَلٰی بَنِیْ اِسْرَاۗئِیْلَ، اَكَلُوْا مِنْهَا وَكَفَرُوْا بِهَا، اَللّٰهُمَّ اَنْزِلْهَا عَلَیْنَا فَاِنَّا بِهَا مُؤْمِنُوْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreen